[SN]TITLE[SN]
Two held after Newport man, 19, left in critical condition

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Two people have been arrested after a man was left in a critical condition following an incident in Newport.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gwent Police was called to Edward VII Avenue at about 22:10 GMT on New Year's Eve.
The 19-year-old suffered serious injuries and was taken to Cardiff's University Hospital of Wales.
